</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Bromsgrove Industries, the West Midlands-based engineer, is paying Pounds
1.48m for Gainsborough, a precision machinist which concentrates on the
aerospace sector.
The consideration comprises Pounds 575,000 cash, Pounds 650,000 of nil
interest loan notes payable next June and 241,546 new shares - Pounds 50,000
in shares is deferred until next June.
