double the cost of those for the existing analogue network.
Monthly charges for access to the Vodafone network are unchanged at Pounds
25 for standard-rate customers, and Pounds 15 for low-user customers who pay
higher call charges. MetroDigital will charge a Pounds 20-a-month access
fee, EuroDigital Pounds 27.50.
The new digital network will have capacity for 175,000 subscribers at its
launch, rising to 2m by 2000. The existing network has 838,000 subscribers,
which Vodafone expects to rise to over 1m later this year.
</TEXT>
