FT  16 JUN 93 / World Stock Markets: Brazil
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
SAO PAULO closed 1.6 per cent higher in heavy trading after investors
reacted positively to the austerity measures announced by the Brazilian
government on Monday night. The Bovespa index was 730 firmer at 45,893.
